						<summary>

						<p>Pāṇḍya, Jaṭāvarman Sundarapāṇḍya, 13th year = c. 13th Century.</p>						

						<p>Much damaged. Seems to record a sale of temple land by the trustees of Tiruvēṅgai-vāchal temple to a Pāṇḍiyadēvar who endowed the same in the temple for a perpetual lamp.</p>						

